I've called Judge Forrest and asked her

09:18.578 --> 09:20.517
to make room in 
her schedule for tomorrow.

09:20.518 --> 09:22.747
If you'd like to have the case seen then,

09:22.748 --> 09:23.955
- we can... 
- Yes, absolutely.

09:23.956 --> 09:26.753
I don't want this hanging over
Olivia for six to eight weeks.

