13:16.263 --> 13:18.074
Yeah. Maybe it would help.

13:19.684 --> 13:20.893
All right.

13:21.039 --> 13:22.040
Okay.

13:22.404 --> 13:23.875
Then that's what we'll do,

13:24.318 --> 13:25.535
right after we finish this.

13:29.938 --> 13:33.202
Wow. Okay, so, um, you...
